# Tests Requirements (Linux)

This document lists required dependencies to run project tests successfully on Linux.

## 1) Core requirements

- Linux machine (Ubuntu/Debian/Fedora/Amazon Linux)
- Git
- Node.js **18.x** (recommended)
- npm **9.x or newer**
- Internet access for first-time dependency/browser install

Check versions:

```bash
node -v
npm -v
git --version

